lead_paragraph: Fernando Llorente's two injury-time goals saw Swansea come from behind to snatch a thrilling 5-4 win over Crystal Palace in an amazing see-saw game at the Liberty Stadium, snapping an 11-game winless streak and handing the Eagles their sixth straight defeat.

headline.print_headline: Swansea Stun Palace With Last-Gasp Winner in 5-4 Thriller
